reviewText: This movie is made of several short stories..  Yeah, there are some erotic scenes but overall the movie is too slow and long to be actually entertaining.  I can understand why reviewers were falling asleep.  It just keeps dragging on and on.

Very poor editing for this film.  At parts it linger for 15 minutes plus without furthering the plot.  In fact, I still don't know what is the point of this film, or even if it has a point at all.
